snippet.title: Riot, fire & teargas at Greek refugee camp after police reportedly hit child

localized.description:
Riots broke out at Moria refugee centre on Lesbos island, Tuesday, with refugees setting rubbish cans on fire and throwing stones at police, who in turn responded with tear gas. Reports from inside the centre state that the violence was sparked by authorities striking a minor.
